## Summary
This documentation explains how Compass uses correlation to identify predictive user behaviors, with values ranging from -1 to 1 and categorized from "Not Predictive" to "Highly Predictive," and demonstrates how to create cohorts from Compass results to compare retention metrics with detailed statistics.

